In simple words, the speaker is talking about an artificial intelligence model called ChatGPT. It can generate text based on the prompts fed to it. The speaker is interested in focusing on the system behind ChatGPT, known as a Transformer-based language model. This language model uses a system called the Transformer that was initially created for translations but has since been used widely in AI. It's a complex system, but the speaker would like to train a version of it.